OL,3,CProposition to remove Jersey Bailiff
OL,4,Cfrom States Assembly withdrawn
OL,6,F"Nevertheless, it has become apparent
OL,7,Fthis week that, whilst a majority of
OL,8,FStates Members recognise that a move
OL,9,Fto an elected or appointed Speaker is
OL,10,Fan appropriate change, a number of
OL,11,FMembers regrettably feel unable to
OL,12,Fvote according to their conscience on
OL,13,Fthis occasion.
OL,15,F"I do not wish to unnecessarily take
OL,16,Fup the time of the Assembly when the
OL,17,Foutcome of the vote is effectively
OL,18,Falready known."
