OL,3,CProposition to remove Jersey Bailiff
OL,4,Cfrom States Assembly withdrawn
OL,6,FConnetable Jehan says he believes "an
OL,7,Funelected and unaccountable Speaker"
OL,8,Fis not sustainable in a "modern
OL,9,Fdemocracy", but recognised the
OL,10,FBailiff's historical and
OL,11,Fconstitutional importance as the Civid
OL,12,FHead of the island.
OL,14,FBut the Connetable also criticised
OL,15,Fmembers, who he accused of interfering
OL,16,Fwith the timing of the debate.
