OL,3,CProposition to remove Jersey Bailiff
OL,4,Cfrom States Assembly withdrawn
OL,6,FHe explains: "I was disappointed with
OL,7,Fthe events in the Assembly (...) some
OL,8,FMembers who are opposed to my
OL,9,Fproposition sought to interfere with
OL,10,Fthe timing of the debate without
OL,11,Fconsulting me, despite it being lodged
OL,12,Fin good order.
OL,14,F"I have been surprised that many
OL,15,FStates Members aren't aware of Article
OL,16,F3 of the States of Jersey Law which
OL,17,Falready allows for a States Member to
OL,18,FChair the Assembly.
